<br>
I am now 57 so unfortunately the warriors are 90% light blue.  They were great up through 56 though.<br>
<br>
Oh, one problem.  Periodically, Lightbringer will spawn which is level 50.  Very easy to chain pets and kill him but ONLY with the air pet.  Maybe others have had better success with other pets, but without crack, I would run out of mana summoning earth, fire or water.  Using the air pet I would finish with 2 bubs of mana. Go figure.  The air pet does a great job of stunning Lightbringer (I think he is a pally and heals himself when down to about 1/3 or 1/4 health).<br>
<br>
I haven't found any other afk camps yet, except the brownies in lfay. <p><img src=http://a5.cpimg.com/image/AD/05/10888365-0078-00E1011E-.jpg"border=0"<br>
